                <Header>Contact Information</Header>
                <Paragraph>The "Contact Us" web page has an electronic message box that allows visitors to send a comment or suggestion or to ask a question. Replies from the USIP are sent via email. The USIP postal address and phone number are also located at the bottom of the "Contac Us" page.</Paragraph>
